org.omg.space.xtce

Class SequenceEntryType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.omg.space.xtce.SequenceEntryType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayParameterRefEntryType, CommandContainerEntryListType.ArgumentRefEntry, CommandContainerEntryListType.FixedValueEntry, ContainerRefEntryType, ContainerSegmentRefEntryType, IndirectParameterRefEntryType, ParameterRefEntryType, ParameterSegmentRefEntryType, StreamSegmentEntryType

    public class SequenceEntryType
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract type used by sequence containers. An entry contains a location in the container. The location may be either fixed or dynamic, absolute (to the start or end of the enclosing container, or relative (to either the previous or subsequent entry). Entries may also repeat.
